  "detailed_description": "Help Puzzled Cat use jetpacks, portals, bombs, gum, and more to conquer treacherous platforming stages.  Play your own way using save states to explore a world full of challenges and secrets - but can you find the way through? Travel through time and space and reach enlightenment.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2650350/extras/6a80c535b8c3f6471975a068910a002a.poster.avif?t=1759932836\" width=616 height=616 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2650350/extras/6a80c535b8c3f6471975a068910a002a.webm?t=1759932836\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2650350/extras/6a80c535b8c3f6471975a068910a002a.mp4?t=1759932836\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>Save states mean you can experiment and figure out exactly how to solve any task. Try things out without losing progress.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2650350/extras/ffa583eee12ae074931b5c5c75bae0a1.poster.avif?t=1759932836\" width=616 height=600 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2650350/extras/ffa583eee12ae074931b5c5c75bae0a1.webm?t=1759932836\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2650350/extras/ffa583eee12ae074931b5c5c75bae0a1.mp4?t=1759932836\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>Explore and you'll find hidden collectibles, levels, and more. There are many ways to tackle the world's hidden challenges.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2650350/extras/39639a1b3af369cc4b11882ce605ccba.poster.avif?t=1759932836\" width=616 height=616 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2650350/extras/39639a1b3af369cc4b11882ce605ccba.webm?t=1759932836\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2650350/extras/39639a1b3af369cc4b11882ce605ccba.mp4?t=1759932836\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>Practice makes perfect, and perfect play has its own rewards.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2650350/extras/1ce6a61a7451864c50b24529e7a4e253.poster.avif?t=1759932836\" width=616 height=616 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2650350/extras/1ce6a61a7451864c50b24529e7a4e253.webm?t=1759932836\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2650350/extras/1ce6a61a7451864c50b24529e7a4e253.mp4?t=1759932836\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>Over 150 levels to explore and multiple endings to find.</li><li>Use save states, or don't! Focus on puzzles, precision, or exploration.</li><li>Cat!</li></ul>",
  "about_the_game": "Help Puzzled Cat use jetpacks, portals, bombs, gum, and more to conquer treacherous platforming stages.  Play your own way using save states to explore a world full of challenges and secrets - but can you find the way through? Travel through time and space and reach enlightenment.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2650350/extras/6a80c535b8c3f6471975a068910a002a.poster.avif?t=1759932836\" width=616 height=616 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2650350/extras/6a80c535b8c3f6471975a068910a002a.webm?t=1759932836\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2650350/extras/6a80c535b8c3f6471975a068910a002a.mp4?t=1759932836\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>Save states mean you can experiment and figure out exactly how to solve any task. Try things out without losing progress.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2650350/extras/ffa583eee12ae074931b5c5c75bae0a1.poster.avif?t=1759932836\" width=616 height=600 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2650350/extras/ffa583eee12ae074931b5c5c75bae0a1.webm?t=1759932836\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2650350/extras/ffa583eee12ae074931b5c5c75bae0a1.mp4?t=1759932836\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>Explore and you'll find hidden collectibles, levels, and more. There are many ways to tackle the world's hidden challenges.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2650350/extras/39